Elizabeth_Lavenza http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elizabeth_Lavenza 0 Elizabeth Frankenstein (née Lavenza) is a fictional character first introduced in Mary Shelley's 1818 novel Frankenstein; or, The Modern Prometheus. In both the novel and its various film adaptations, she is the fiancée of Victor Frankenstein.
